{
  "texts": [
    "Removal of words such as out, no, and, and the letters l, e, and s may be useful in a nontechnical scenario but are very important in the context of MWOs.",
    "In this case, the letters l and e state that the part to be installed is along the leading edge panel.",
    "Stop word removal also removes the word no, by assuming that it is used to convey negation, when in reality it is short hand for \"number\" in the context of this MWO.",
    "The next step of text cleaning performs some basic operations such as punctuation and special character removal, and lower casing of the text string.",
    "This step removes the punctuation mark used for forward slash (\"/\"), and also removes the numbers 2 and 5 that are used to identify the panels."
  ]
}